{"type": "article", "id": 27811, "title": "可以发亮的书签", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-06T06:57:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 97, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162339rLiJyQG60ObcI7ez.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>打算看书但又不想打扰枕边人休息的话，你可能需要这款可以发亮的书签。Bookmark light 由来自 <a href=\"http://www.kyouei-ltd.co.jp/\">kyouei design</a> 的设计师 Kouichi Okamoto 同东京大学的 AgIC 商业投资公司合作打造。书签上有着由导电油墨和薄纽扣电池组成的电路，将上下两端的电视扣在一起，就会点亮书签上的 LED 灯。书签采用液晶体薄膜制成，你可以清晰地看到上面的电路，有一种 geek 的感觉。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/bookmark-light-kyouei-design-06-02-2016/\">购买链接</a>，售价为 16 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162336WjuwR7A8NdYPxIlm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021623377mj0U9cqQXJhLpYD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162338Qf8g3A5TYFSWEUMt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162338pc6uo9O5EzCyrWNj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}